    "Such oversight could have serious consequences for the patient, who may not receive the correct treatment in a timely manner.",
    "Overall, there is a significant risk for large language models to produce ungrounded or unverified medical advice.",
    "It is necessary to raise awareness of this new challenge in the AGIlandscape.",
